00:08:38.387 --> 00:08:40.220
they have enough business
or enough patients

00:08:40.220 --> 00:08:40.969
from other places.

00:08:40.969 --> 00:08:42.915
And Medicare's a plan
that's got its rules,

00:08:42.915 --> 00:08:44.290
and you have to
follow the rules.

00:08:44.290 --> 00:08:45.892
And some people
think that Medicare

00:08:45.892 --> 00:08:47.850
doesn't pay as well as
other options they have.

00:08:47.850 --> 00:08:49.107
So there are a few.

00:08:49.107 --> 00:08:50.690
Most of the doctors,
the vast majority

00:08:50.690 --> 00:08:52.470
of doctors in the country,
will work with Medicare.

