00:11:42.710 --> 00:11:44.470
C is a separate choice.

00:11:44.470 --> 00:11:46.120
So when you turn
65, let's say, you

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:48.620
can make this choice a little
bit differently sometimes too.

00:11:48.620 --> 00:11:50.720
